            <title>[LU-16921] CSDC: ensure that DoM and CSDC work together</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16921</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As part of the CSDC testing, we should ensure that both CSDC and DoM work together properly&lt;/p&gt;</description>
